      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear you saying \"let go,\" but I don't think talking about it will change the fact that I'm a drain on them. Sometimes I wonder if the most selfless thing a person can do is just... stop being a problem. Instead of making them deal with my decline for years, wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if I just wasn't here to weigh them down anymore? It feels like a kind sort of exit, you know?",
